media.altText:
Another week has passed
time slipping by
going too fast

I wish just once I could stand still
To find a moment
A pause
To catch my breath
A solid footing

But no
Its indifference overwhelming
Time keeps going 
Wearing me down

So I take my pill 
I dismiss my frown
I try again

Maybe this time I can do better
Achieve something 
Be of value

But probably not
